Issues.Body:
In RC1 `DrawBorder` no longer renders `ButtonBorderStyle.Dotted` and `ButtonBorderStyle.Dashed` correctly. Sample code:

``` C#
            ControlPaint.DrawBorder(e.Graphics, bounds, Color.Red, ButtonBorderStyle.Dotted);
            bounds.Offset(0, 30);
            ControlPaint.DrawBorder(e.Graphics, bounds, Color.Green, ButtonBorderStyle.Dashed);
```

Current is on the left, correct is on the right:

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8184940/93552521-79281e80-f925-11ea-8d80-dee9e2a72920.png)
